1
00:01:11,520 --> 00:01:12,120
Ling'er!

2
00:01:17,600 --> 00:01:18,920
I sacrifice my soul...

3
00:01:19,240 --> 00:01:20,700
...to infuse your spirit.

4
00:01:21,200 --> 00:01:22,520
Protect my people...

5
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:26,120
...and bless the world.

6
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,720
Ling'er.

7
00:01:39,400 --> 00:01:39,960
Ling'er.

8
00:01:42,360 --> 00:01:43,800
Live on.

9
00:01:43,800 --> 00:01:44,479
Ling'er!

10
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:45,600
Ling'er!

11
00:02:53,760 --> 00:02:55,290
What exactly is that thing?

12
00:02:56,079 --> 00:02:57,740
It's actually faster than me.

13
00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:00,360
I've never lost a race.

14
00:03:08,480 --> 00:03:10,160
Is there something wrong with the seal?

15
00:03:10,160 --> 00:03:13,420
Why is the malevolent energy inside me becoming unstable?

16
00:03:27,920 --> 00:03:28,720
Ling'er.

17
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,079
Kunmi.

18
00:03:35,200 --> 00:03:37,260
Why does that name sound so familiar?

19
00:04:01,080 --> 00:04:02,240
Little lady.

20
00:04:03,560 --> 00:04:05,020
Why are you here all alone?

21
00:04:05,120 --> 00:04:06,380
I can't find my family.

22
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:07,120
Is that so?

23
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:09,050
Come home with big brother.

24
00:04:09,440 --> 00:04:10,480
Where did this pervert come from?

25
00:04:10,480 --> 00:04:12,400
Get lost if you don't want a beating.

26
00:04:12,400 --> 00:04:13,680
Feisty.

27
00:04:14,240 --> 00:04:16,000
I like it.

28
00:04:18,079 --> 00:04:20,010
Why can't I use my spiritual power?

29
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:22,960
These little hands are so smooth.

30
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:24,320
Give me a kiss.

31
00:04:24,320 --> 00:04:25,120
Stay back!

32
00:04:28,680 --> 00:04:29,210
Who is it?

33
00:04:29,520 --> 00:04:30,780
Who dares spoil my fun?

34
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:34,360
You can't see me standing right here in broad daylight?

35
00:04:34,840 --> 00:04:36,640
Who is it? Stop sneaking around!

36
00:04:36,920 --> 00:04:37,600
Come out if you have the guts!

37
00:04:37,600 --> 00:04:39,120
Stop playing tricks!

38
00:04:39,640 --> 00:04:41,170
Do I look like a god to you...

39
00:04:41,440 --> 00:04:43,040
...or a ghost?

40
00:04:45,240 --> 00:04:47,240
You... are you human or ghost?

41
00:04:54,280 --> 00:04:55,200
Little sister.

42
00:04:55,320 --> 00:04:57,440
Don't walk into corners like this in the future.

43
00:04:57,440 --> 00:04:59,000
The human world is a mixed bag.

44
00:04:59,000 --> 00:05:00,080
Their hearts are unpredictable.

45
00:05:00,080 --> 00:05:02,340
Sister, how can you use spiritual power?

46
00:05:02,800 --> 00:05:04,080
This place is Kunmi.

47
00:05:04,440 --> 00:05:06,080
To prevent demons from causing trouble,

48
00:05:06,080 --> 00:05:08,360
my sworn brother specifically set up a barrier here.

49
00:05:08,360 --> 00:05:11,080
No one can use spiritual power without registering first.

50
00:05:11,080 --> 00:05:12,560
I have to register?

51
00:05:12,920 --> 00:05:14,400
Where do I go to register?

52
00:05:14,760 --> 00:05:16,880
Then what if I go out to play later...

53
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:18,640
...and run into bad guys?

54
00:05:22,840 --> 00:05:25,080
Holding this jade pendant counts as registering.

55
00:05:25,080 --> 00:05:27,480
However, you must not hurt the common people.

56
00:05:27,480 --> 00:05:29,720
Otherwise, I'll have to punish you.

57
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:31,680
Thank you, sister. You're so kind.

58
00:05:31,680 --> 00:05:32,400
By the way, sister,

59
00:05:32,400 --> 00:05:34,159
I still don't know your name.

60
00:05:34,240 --> 00:05:35,500
Just call me Qingluan.

61
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:36,440
And you?

62
00:05:37,200 --> 00:05:38,000
Me?

63
00:05:39,400 --> 00:05:40,930
I think I'm called Ling'er.

64
00:05:41,720 --> 00:05:42,520
You think?

65
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:44,360
A name is a name.

66
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:45,840
What do you mean 'think'?

67
00:05:46,400 --> 00:05:48,760
Because when I was dazed,

68
00:05:48,960 --> 00:05:51,280
I kept hearing someone call me Ling'er.

69
00:05:51,440 --> 00:05:53,360
But after I struggled to wake up,

70
00:05:53,800 --> 00:05:55,440
I couldn't remember anything.

71
00:05:55,440 --> 00:05:57,240
My head hurts when I try to think.

72
00:05:58,200 --> 00:06:00,200
So, I should be called Ling'er.

73
00:06:01,560 --> 00:06:03,280
If you can't remember, then forget it.

74
00:06:03,280 --> 00:06:05,200
Maybe it was something bad anyway.

75
00:06:05,200 --> 00:06:08,000
Do you have a place to stay in Kunmi?

76
00:06:09,280 --> 00:06:12,280
I chased a ball of light and stumbled here by accident.

77
00:06:12,520 --> 00:06:14,200
I'm not a stranger to the people, but the place is strange.

78
00:06:14,200 --> 00:06:16,120
So I don't know where to stay either.

79
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:17,720
"Not a stranger to the people, but the place is strange"?

80
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:19,180
What kind of logic is that?

81
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,800
Since you are all alone

82
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,160
and have come to my territory,

83
00:06:22,160 --> 00:06:23,800
I'll look after you from now on.

84
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,800
Thank you, Sister.

85
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,400
By the way,

86
00:06:25,480 --> 00:06:28,200
let me show you around Kunmi.

87
00:06:28,280 --> 00:06:28,840
Let's go.

88
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:40,640
Sister,

89
00:06:41,040 --> 00:06:42,720
I want to find my memories.

90
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:45,120
I want to know who I am.

91
00:06:46,040 --> 00:06:47,300
Looking for memories?

92
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:49,060
Actually, sometimes,

93
00:06:49,360 --> 00:06:51,620
forgetting is better than remembering.

94
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:54,440
That might be true,

95
00:06:55,640 --> 00:06:57,360
but since I was born in this world,

96
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:59,680
my past is part of who I am.

97
00:07:00,040 --> 00:07:01,360
Even the bad parts,

98
00:07:02,520 --> 00:07:04,250
are things I have experienced.

99
00:07:04,360 --> 00:07:06,490
I don't want to live in a daze like this.

100
00:07:06,800 --> 00:07:08,400
I want to retrieve

101
00:07:09,600 --> 00:07:11,360
the memories lost in my mind.

102
00:07:12,880 --> 00:07:14,520
My sworn brother is knowledgeable

103
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:15,840
and knows the Spiritual Probe technique.

104
00:07:15,840 --> 00:07:17,400
Why don't I take you to see him?

105
00:07:17,400 --> 00:07:18,530
Your sworn brother?

106
00:07:18,760 --> 00:07:19,820
You might not know,

107
00:07:19,880 --> 00:07:22,160
but he is the famous King of Kunmi.

108
00:07:22,280 --> 00:07:23,400
The King of Kunmi?

109
00:07:23,880 --> 00:07:24,880
Sister Qingluan,

110
00:07:25,040 --> 00:07:26,840
you took a human as your sworn brother?

111
00:07:26,840 --> 00:07:27,880
Not exactly.

112
00:07:28,560 --> 00:07:31,080
When we came to Kunmi a thousand years ago,

113
00:07:31,440 --> 00:07:32,800
demons ran rampant here.

114
00:07:32,800 --> 00:07:34,159
Dark energy overflowed,

115
00:07:34,159 --> 00:07:35,620
making it uninhabitable.

116
00:07:36,280 --> 00:07:37,000
So,

117
00:07:37,040 --> 00:07:39,720
my brother led me to slay demons,

118
00:07:39,760 --> 00:07:41,020
purge the dark energy,

119
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:43,010
and restore peace to this land.

120
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,560
Also, using his great powers,

121
00:07:45,560 --> 00:07:47,840
he set up many magical arrays

122
00:07:48,040 --> 00:07:51,080
to block outside entities from entering Kunmi.

123
00:07:51,159 --> 00:07:54,560
Grateful for his protection,

124
00:07:54,760 --> 00:07:56,640
the people honored him as

125
00:07:57,240 --> 00:07:58,080
the King of Kunmi.

126
00:07:58,080 --> 00:08:01,000
That's amazing. You're amazing too, Sister Qingluan.

127
00:08:01,000 --> 00:08:02,660
With such a powerful brother,

128
00:08:02,760 --> 00:08:04,480
you can walk around like you own the place.

129
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:04,940
Come on.

130
00:08:05,200 --> 00:08:06,320
Unlike me,

131
00:08:07,040 --> 00:08:08,570
my cultivation is shallow.

132
00:08:09,880 --> 00:08:10,960
That's easy.

133
00:08:11,440 --> 00:08:12,560
Let's become sworn sisters.

134
00:08:12,560 --> 00:08:14,620
Then my brother will be your brother.

135
00:08:15,560 --> 00:08:17,960
I couldn't possibly...

136
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,840
When do we start?

137
00:08:20,880 --> 00:08:21,560
Hey,

138
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,680
let this be our witness.

139
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,680
From now on, we are sisters.

140
00:08:30,240 --> 00:08:32,400
Not that. It breaks too easily.

141
00:08:34,200 --> 00:08:35,240
This one works.

142
00:08:35,320 --> 00:08:36,720
Our bond should be like this,

143
00:08:36,720 --> 00:08:37,799
unbreakable.

144
00:08:38,320 --> 00:08:40,240
Okay. Let it witness this today.

145
00:08:40,640 --> 00:08:42,700
From now on, you are my little sister.

146
00:08:42,880 --> 00:08:43,480
Sister.

147
00:08:43,840 --> 00:08:44,600
Little Sister.

148
00:08:44,600 --> 00:08:45,360
Sister.

149
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:46,120
Little Sister.

150
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:46,920
Sister!

151
00:09:06,160 --> 00:09:08,400
I lost control and drank too much.

152
00:09:08,680 --> 00:09:10,680
I didn't make a fool of myself, did I?

153
00:09:12,560 --> 00:09:13,440
Come on, come on!

154
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,770
Let's check over there.

155
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:16,000
Hurry up, come here!

156
00:09:16,120 --> 00:09:17,560
So noisy...

157
00:09:26,480 --> 00:09:27,920
So soft.

158
00:09:32,240 --> 00:09:33,840
Ling'er, what are you doing?

159
00:09:38,080 --> 00:09:38,960
Miss Qingluan,

160
00:09:39,080 --> 00:09:40,880
why do you play such tricks on us?

161
00:09:42,120 --> 00:09:43,560
I didn't.

162
00:09:44,000 --> 00:09:44,920
I can testify.

163
00:09:45,240 --> 00:09:46,600
It wasn't Sister Qingluan.

164
00:09:46,600 --> 00:09:47,320
It was me.

165
00:09:48,880 --> 00:09:50,880
The Heavenly Clan is about to hold the Hundred Flowers Festival.

166
00:09:50,880 --> 00:09:53,320
We were ordered to come here to pick flowers.

167
00:09:53,320 --> 00:09:55,250
We informed King Kunmi in advance,

168
00:09:55,520 --> 00:09:57,120
and King Kunmi permitted it.

169
00:09:57,120 --> 00:09:58,760
Miss Qingluan, if you are dissatisfied,

170
00:09:58,760 --> 00:10:00,600
you could have just told us directly.

171
00:10:00,600 --> 00:10:02,240
Why go to the trouble of teasing us?

172
00:10:02,240 --> 00:10:03,760
I really didn't.

173
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,360
Since Miss Qingluan claims ignorance of this matter,

174
00:10:06,360 --> 00:10:07,560
and teased us for no reason,

175
00:10:07,560 --> 00:10:08,400
then today,

176
00:10:08,800 --> 00:10:11,060
we must go to Cloud Deep to find King Kunmi

177
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,920
and ask him to give the Heavenly Clan an explanation.

178
00:10:12,920 --> 00:10:13,440
Hey, hey.

179
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:14,760
Let's go.

180
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,000
Oh no, oh no.

181
00:10:17,000 --> 00:10:18,000
This is bad, this is bad.

182
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,920
Did I cause trouble?

183
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:23,560
You don't know my sworn brother. He's incredibly rigid.

184
00:10:23,560 --> 00:10:24,400
If he finds out

185
00:10:24,520 --> 00:10:26,120
that I was naughty and caused trouble again,

186
00:10:26,120 --> 00:10:28,040
he will definitely punish me severely.

187
00:10:28,040 --> 00:10:29,360
Your sworn brother is that harsh?

188
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,290
What a headache.

189
00:10:30,880 --> 00:10:31,880
What should we do?

190
00:10:32,920 --> 00:10:34,160
Let me think.

191
00:10:34,520 --> 00:10:35,360
Let me think.

192
00:10:36,680 --> 00:10:37,320
Aha!

193
00:10:37,920 --> 00:10:38,800
I've got it.

194
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:42,540
I can disguise you as my sworn brother to send them away.

195
00:10:43,240 --> 00:10:44,320
Will that work?

196
00:10:44,360 --> 00:10:45,360
Of course it will.

197
00:10:45,520 --> 00:10:47,800
Anyway, you both have the aura of the Dragon Clan.

198
00:10:47,800 --> 00:10:50,800
Besides, my sworn brother is often in seclusion for cultivation,

199
00:10:50,800 --> 00:10:52,930
so you won't be exposed just this once.

200
00:10:53,760 --> 00:10:56,640
Good sister, please help me.

201
00:10:56,840 --> 00:10:57,840
Sister.

202
00:10:57,920 --> 00:11:00,400
Okay, okay. I suppose I can.

203
00:11:00,560 --> 00:11:02,320
Since that works, let's go now.

204
00:11:03,080 --> 00:11:04,000
Sister.

205
00:11:04,120 --> 00:11:05,120
Sister Qingluan.

206
00:11:19,120 --> 00:11:20,200
Sister Qingluan.

207
00:11:20,560 --> 00:11:22,360
I'm here. Don't blow your cover.

208
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:27,160
King Kunmi.

209
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:34,480
We have heard that King Kunmi

210
00:11:34,480 --> 00:11:36,280
manages his subordinates well,

211
00:11:36,560 --> 00:11:39,420
but your sworn sister surprisingly has no manners.

212
00:11:42,120 --> 00:11:43,040
My sister is mischievous.

213
00:11:43,040 --> 00:11:44,300
On behalf of Qingluan,

214
00:11:44,520 --> 00:11:46,250
I apologize to all the fairies.

215
00:11:47,040 --> 00:11:47,370
Also,

216
00:11:47,760 --> 00:11:49,200
I will certainly punish Qingluan severely,

217
00:11:49,200 --> 00:11:51,040
to give the fairies of the Heavenly Clan

218
00:11:51,040 --> 00:11:51,970
an explanation.

219
00:11:56,600 --> 00:11:58,120
We hope King Kunmi

220
00:11:58,520 --> 00:11:59,600
keeps his word.

221
00:12:18,160 --> 00:12:18,680
Sister.

222
00:12:18,680 --> 00:12:20,520
My sworn brother isn't as gentle as you.

223
00:12:20,520 --> 00:12:21,780
He is very protective.

224
00:12:21,840 --> 00:12:23,440
Well, we were in the wrong.

225
00:12:23,600 --> 00:12:24,400
Besides,

226
00:12:24,760 --> 00:12:27,000
I don't believe that sworn brother of yours

227
00:12:27,000 --> 00:12:28,880
wouldn't be moved by seeing so many fairies.

228
00:12:28,880 --> 00:12:30,520
Then you really don't know.

229
00:12:30,800 --> 00:12:33,000
There are thousands of beauties in this world,

230
00:12:33,000 --> 00:12:34,000
but my sworn brother

231
00:12:34,000 --> 00:12:35,600
only has eyes for one person.

232
00:12:36,080 --> 00:12:37,680
Am I really as good as you say?

233
00:12:37,680 --> 00:12:38,520
Of course.

234
00:12:43,080 --> 00:12:44,040
Oh no, oh no.

235
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:49,360
Brother.

236
00:12:49,480 --> 00:12:51,360
Why are you here?

237
00:12:51,760 --> 00:12:53,960
What trouble have you caused this time?

238
00:12:54,400 --> 00:12:56,080
Not at all.

239
00:12:56,320 --> 00:12:58,160
Just playing around.

240
00:13:09,440 --> 00:13:10,120
Ling'er.

241
00:13:13,200 --> 00:13:14,320
King Kunmi.

242
00:13:17,720 --> 00:13:18,520
Ling'er.

243
00:13:19,520 --> 00:13:20,520
Is it really you?

244
00:13:20,760 --> 00:13:21,760
Do you know me?

245
00:13:29,760 --> 00:13:30,620
Sworn brother.

246
00:13:30,680 --> 00:13:31,560
King Kunmi.

247
00:13:31,960 --> 00:13:32,890
Are you alright?

248
00:13:33,240 --> 00:13:34,440
Do you really know me?

249
00:13:39,920 --> 00:13:40,480
I'm fine.

250
00:13:42,320 --> 00:13:43,080
I don't.

251
00:13:52,520 --> 00:13:53,580
What is happening?

252
00:13:54,680 --> 00:13:57,240
Why does my heart hurt so much?

253
00:14:11,920 --> 00:14:13,520
How about I call you Yun Yuan?

254
00:14:15,680 --> 00:14:16,340
King Kunmi.

255
00:14:17,840 --> 00:14:18,840
Do you know me?

256
00:14:25,600 --> 00:14:26,130
Yue Ying.

257
00:14:28,280 --> 00:14:28,810
General.

258
00:14:29,680 --> 00:14:31,940
Return to the Dragon Tribe immediately.

259
00:14:32,000 --> 00:14:32,560
Yes, sir.

260
00:14:50,800 --> 00:14:53,120
Over here. After him!

261
00:15:42,280 --> 00:15:45,280
I can't believe there's a purple dragon in this world.

262
00:15:47,320 --> 00:15:48,400
What is your name?

263
00:15:50,160 --> 00:15:51,220
I don't have a name.

264
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:55,040
How about I give you a name?

265
00:15:56,840 --> 00:15:58,720
The purple air comes from the east,

266
00:15:58,720 --> 00:16:00,120
like clouds in the sky,

267
00:16:01,280 --> 00:16:02,740
like a dragon in the abyss.

268
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,680
Why don't I call you Yun Yuan?

269
00:16:07,840 --> 00:16:09,240
Clouds in the sky.

270
00:16:10,040 --> 00:16:11,200
Dragon in the abyss.

271
00:16:12,200 --> 00:16:13,000
Yun Yuan.

272
00:16:13,920 --> 00:16:16,080
Okay. I'll be Yun Yuan.

273
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:18,360
Yun Yuan, it's not safe here.

274
00:16:18,960 --> 00:16:20,090
Let me take you away.

275
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:24,960
Okay.

276
00:16:25,800 --> 00:16:26,840
I'll go with you.

277
00:16:40,320 --> 00:16:40,960
Ling'er.

278
00:16:42,160 --> 00:16:43,920
Why have you forgotten me?

279
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:48,280
A golden horse has appeared!

280
00:16:48,280 --> 00:16:49,880
This is a sign of good fortune from the heavens.

281
00:16:49,880 --> 00:16:51,960
We must soak up this good luck.

282
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:54,320
Yes, yes, indeed.

283
00:16:56,120 --> 00:16:57,080
Golden horse.

284
00:17:08,560 --> 00:17:09,400
Who are you?

285
00:17:10,079 --> 00:17:11,160
Do you know me?

286
00:17:11,560 --> 00:17:12,160
Princess.

287
00:17:13,040 --> 00:17:13,839
Princess.

288
00:17:15,560 --> 00:17:17,800
Look at me. What part of me looks like a princess?

289
00:17:17,800 --> 00:17:19,319
Do you have the wrong person?

290
00:17:19,319 --> 00:17:21,650
The Princess doesn't remember me either.

291
00:17:22,040 --> 00:17:23,000
I am Yue Ying.

292
00:17:23,160 --> 00:17:24,400
May I ask your name, Miss?

293
00:17:24,400 --> 00:17:25,599
Just call me Ling'er.

294
00:17:25,720 --> 00:17:26,359
Yue Ying.

295
00:17:26,560 --> 00:17:29,220
Di Yun will face a trial. Protect him carefully.

296
00:17:29,360 --> 00:17:30,760
To avoid any complications.

297
00:17:30,760 --> 00:17:31,560
Yue Ying.

298
00:17:32,240 --> 00:17:33,200
Yue Ying.

299
00:17:34,920 --> 00:17:35,840
I was ordered

300
00:17:35,920 --> 00:17:38,360
to secretly protect the Heavenly Emperor's son during his mortal trial.

301
00:17:38,360 --> 00:17:40,800
Even the Heavenly Emperor's son has to undergo mortal trials now?

302
00:17:40,800 --> 00:17:42,120
It's not exactly a trial.

303
00:17:42,120 --> 00:17:44,780
I heard this lord refused an arranged marriage.

304
00:17:44,920 --> 00:17:47,600
He didn't want to marry that unruly Dragon Princess,

305
00:17:47,600 --> 00:17:49,200
so he came down to the mortal realm.

306
00:17:49,200 --> 00:17:51,360
The Heavenly Emperor has urged him to return many times,

307
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:53,120
but he'd rather roam this world

308
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:54,860
than go back and marry her.

309
00:18:03,360 --> 00:18:04,560
You have some nerve, Son of the Heavenly Emperor.

310
00:18:04,560 --> 00:18:06,560
Treating the Dragon Princess like this.

311
00:18:06,560 --> 00:18:08,640
I'm going to teach you a lesson on her behalf.
